features: WHAT YOU GET: 80 sheets of winter Christmas snowflake letterheads, plenty enough for your crafting and greeting needs.

UNIQUE DESIGN: Blue as the main color with winter snowflakes, Christmas trees and other elements, unique style, dreamy and romantic, perfect for winter and white Christmas background paper, decoration paper, letterhead and printing background paper.

PROPER SIZE: Each sheet measures 8.5 x 11 inch, and the letterhead leaves enough blank sections for you to write your best wishes and greetings, which is very thoughtful. Dimensions are measured manually, please allow for errors.
DURABLE MATERIAL: Our writing paper is made of good quality paper, the paper is textured, durable and reliable, with clear patterns and smooth writing, and can be used for printing.

WIDE APPLICATION: Perfect for letters, greeting cards, party invitations, office supplies, school supplies, suitable for everyone, especially teenagers. They are wonderful letterheads to send to your family, friends, and even Santa Claus.
